{"arkId":"cl010102256","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010102256","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Enfant couch\u00e9 se tenant la t\u00eate","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Enfant couch\u00e9 se tenant la t\u00eate"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1800 - 1825 (bibliographie\/travail de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1800,"endYear":1825,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"TH 154","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statuette","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"L\u0027enfant est couch\u00e9 sur le dos. D\u0027une main, il semble se prot\u00e9ger le visage, ou se masquer les yeux, et de l\u0027autre il tient sur son ventre un fruit (un citron ?). Son attitude correspond plut\u00f4t \u00e0 celle des J\u00e9sus qu\u0027aux putti de tradition flamande. De nombreux exemples sont conserv\u00e9s dans le monde hispanique de ces statuettes isol\u00e9es plac\u00e9es dans un berceau : l\u0027Enfant est repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 dormant, parfois portant le doigt \u00e0 la bouche.\r\nIl est tentant de reconna\u00eetre cet ivoire dans le lot 47 de la vente de la collection du baron Roger \u00e0 Paris en 1841 et 1842 : \u0022Une figure : enfant couch\u00e9 tenant un fruit dans sa main, en ivoire sculpt\u00e9, travail ancien d\u0027une belle ex\u00e9cution ; les jambes ont \u00e9t\u00e9 recoll\u00e9es (dans son \u00e9tui du temps).\u0022 La correspondance iconographique incite \u00e0 cette identification, corrobor\u00e9e par la pr\u00e9cision de l\u0027\u00e9tat de conservation.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; Etiquette au dos : E. 22","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"20,8","displayDimension":"20,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"5,6","displayDimension":"5,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"5,5","displayDimension":"5,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant","placeOfCreation":"Flandres (Europe) (?)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Salomon-Louis, baron Roger; sa vente, Paris, 27 janvier 1842, n\u00b0 47; collection Adolphe Thiers; legs Elise Dosne Thiers, 1880, suivant les volont\u00e9s de son mari et sous r\u00e9serve d\u2019usufruit de sa s\u0153ur F\u00e9licie Dosne qui y renonce et ex\u00e9cute le legs en 1881.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Dosne-Thiers, Elise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Thiers, Louis Adolphe","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Baron Roger, Salomon Louis","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit"}],"place":[{"va